        create:     "Design a fully annotated cross-sectional diagram of skin suitable as a medical student revision resource. Your diagram must include: all five epidermal strata (with cell types and key molecular event at each); papillary and reticular dermis (with structural proteins and receptor types); hypodermis; and at minimum four labelled appendages. Annotate: the site of mitosis, the site of keratinisation onset, the location of the waterproof barrier, and the boundary of 'skin' vs 'not skin.'"
